@import './styles/config.styl'
@require './styles/wrapper.styl'

.page
  padding-bottom 2rem

.page-edit
  @extend $wrapper
  padding-top 1rem
  padding-bottom 1rem
  overflow auto
  .edit-link
    display inline-block
    a
      color lighten($textColor, 25%)
      margin-right 0.25rem
  .last-updated
    float right
    font-size 0.9em
    .prefix
      font-weight 500
      color lighten($textColor, 25%)
    .time
      font-weight 400
      color #aaa

.page-nav
  @extend $wrapper
  padding-top 1rem
  padding-bottom 0
  .inner
    min-height 2rem
    margin-top 0
    border-top 1px solid $borderColor
    padding-top 1rem
    overflow auto // clear float
  .next
    float right

@media (max-width: $MQMobile)
  .page-edit
    .edit-link
      margin-bottom .5rem
    .last-updated
      font-size .8em
      float none
      text-align left
